    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1895-09-07T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1895-09-07T00:00:00-05:00" n="388"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d388">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Adee</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Armstrong</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1895-09-07">
                            <hi rend="italic">September 7, 1895</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Arrangement with Spanish minister here provides for delivery on 15th in
                    Washington of negotiable drafts on London for as many pounds sterling as can be
                    had at current exchange for 1,449,000 United States gold dollars, this sum being
                    taken as equivalent of the one and one-half million Spanish gold pesos which
                    Spain agreed to pay. Note of minister for foreign affairs to you is understood
                    from your telegrams of 5th and to-day to be in accordance with this arrangement,
                    which attorney and counsel for Mora have accepted. If no other verbal variation
                    appears than that stated in your telegram of to-day, you will answer Spanish
                    note as heretofore directed.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Adee</hi>, <hi rend="italic">Acting.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
